Class IpcStop

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcStop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class IpcStop
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains information for a single route. Since Stop objects do not change dynamically this class is not made immutable via a serialization proxy. This simplifies the class greatly.
